These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, white, emerald
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, chess, magic-tricks
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, turtle
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, adventure, western
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, sunflower, iris
 1. the person who growsiris is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 2. the person watching western movies is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 6. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person who likes white is in the middle##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite        | lemonade |
| Color          | emerald    | white        | aquamarine    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks        | board-games        | chess    |
| Pet           | turtle        | chinchilla    | rabbit   |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure    | western | animation |
| Flower     | sunflower     | azalea          | iris     |

