.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, chaman, swisher
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, paramedic, software-developer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, zombie
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, techno, electronic
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, poppy, daffodil
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, soy-milk
1. the electrician is the fan of electronic##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the electrician is on the left of the software-developer##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
5. the blend-smoker is the person drinking fanta##1
6. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the electrician is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
9. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |         3          |
| Cigar         | swisher    | blend     | chaman            |
| Job           | paramedic | electrician | software-developer |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | satire      | zombie             |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | electronic     | techno             |
| Flower         | poppy  | daffodil       | iris           |
| Beverage     | soy-milk     | fanta   | milk            |

