There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, black, chestnut
There are 3 different nationalities: american, british, german
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, iced-tea
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the american##1
 4. the person who likes lilac is in the middle##1
 5. the british is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who likes chestnut##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the tram##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the british is the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |
| Birthday          | september | april | july        |
| Hobby         | fishing  | dancing   | reading     |
| Transport           | jet-ski  | tram | skateboard |
| Color   | chestnut  | lilac   | black     |
