6. the lawyer is on the left of the fan of folk##1
7. the lawyer is on the far left##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is the lawyer##1
9. the person playing chess is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |
| Game          | mah-jongg  | chess       | poker    |
| Nationality         | polish | russian     | spanish      |
| Job           | lawyer  | journalist | scientist    |
