 3. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
 4. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 5. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 6. the person who likes grey is the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person driving the subway##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
10. the person watching family movies is the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing    | woodworking     | magic-tricks         |
| Color          | brown  | blood-red    | grey         |
| Game           | poker | chess | backgammon          |
| Movie-Genre   | family    | spy      | sports        |
| Music-Genre   | salsa     | funk     | rock          |
| Transport         | subway    | boat | motorbike |

