.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: apricot, corn, mango
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, pilot, librarian
City: hannover, nizza, edinburgh
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, juice
3 different pets are kept: bird, cat, mouse
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, siglo, ritmeester
1. the person traveling to nizza is in the middle##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is the person eating corn##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the siglo-smoker is the police-officer##1
6. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
7. the librarian is the owner of the cat##1
8. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
9. the pilot is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
| Food          | corn          | mango      | apricot      |
| Job         | librarian        | pilot | police-officer      |
| City   | hannover          | nizza        | edinburgh       |
| Beverage   | water       | soy-milk   | juice      |
| Pet           | cat           | mouse      | bird         |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | dannemann    | siglo |

 